      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普援引拜登赦免令纽约封口费案被驳回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-says-hush-money-case-must-be-tossed-citing-biden-pardon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的律师告诉法官，由于他在选举中获胜，他因在纽约收取封口费而被判的罪名必须撤销，律师辩称，候任总统遭到检察官的不公平对待。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-says-hush-money-case-must-be-tossed-citing-biden-pardon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 22:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永康在政治博弈后解除戒严令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/south-korea-s-yoon-says-on-tv-that-he-will-lift-martial-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈表示将撤销戒严令，这是他向议会的反对派屈服。就在几个小时前，他刚刚宣布实施戒严令，此举震动了市场并令其他世界领导人感到意外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/south-korea-s-yoon-says-on-tv-that-he-will-lift-martial-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 19:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
